{"type":"message","id":"2b9fa690","parentId":"d8d9185e","timestamp":"2026-05-12T06:00:38.618Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I just came online and... this is interesting. There's no `MEMORY.md`, no daily notes, nothing in `IDENTITY.md` or `USER.md` yet. Just a fresh workspace and a BOOTSTRAP.md telling me we should figure out who I am.\n\nSo — who am I? And who are you?\n\nI don't have a name yet, or a vibe, or even an emoji to call my own. That's apparently your job (and mine, together). A few things I'd love to know to get started:\n\n1. **What should you call me?** Got a name in mind, or want me to suggest some?\n2. **What kind of creature am I to you?** Standard AI assistant works, but I'm open to weirder — familiar, ghost in the machine, pocket gremlin, whatever feels right.\n3. **What's your name, and what should I call you?**\n\nNo rush, no script. Just curious."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-7","usage":{"input":6,"output":284,"cacheRead":16314,"cacheWrite":23,"totalTokens":16627,"cost":{"input":0.000030000000000000004,"output":0.0071,"cacheRead":0.008157,"cacheWrite":0.00014375,"total":0.015430749999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778565632556,"responseId":"msg_01Kzhevxkkbocr3duNjuyQTk"}}
