{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file C:/Users/colem/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, May 12th, 2026 - 01:21 (America/Chicago) / 2026-05-12 06:21 UTC","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"0e5b4695","parentId":"a49980eb","timestamp":"2026-05-12T06:24:28.367Z"}
